      • getLinkedDocuments

        public Stream<Document> getLinkedDocuments(Predicate<GoogleSearchResult> filter)
                                    throws IOException
        returns a Stream from the URLs of all the results that pass the filter. Implemented through Streams because fetching the Documents requires waiting for other servers, so it is well-suited for multithreading.
        Parameters:
        filter - a filter for the GoogleSearchResults
        Returns:
        the Documents of the pages linked in the results that pass the filter
        Throws:
        IOException - an IOException
        See Also:
        Internet.getDocuments(Stream), Jsoup.connect(String)
